items.name: Lunair
items.description: The fastest way to add a video to your landing page. As easy as writing, with creative control. Describe your product or idea and Lunair generates a complete video: consistent characters, custom scenes (not stock assets), voiceover, music, and motion, delivered as a ready-to-share video file. Then edit with plain language: choose a narrator, tweak the script, refine scenes to match your brand. Built for custom, on-brand explainers and marketing videos, not generic AI clips. Join 5,000+ creators.

items.name: Prompt Library
items.tagline: All your best prompts. One shortcut away.
items.description: Save, tag, and organize prompts in collections, then press ‚åò‚å•P to instantly insert them into any app on your Mac.

items.name: Formaly
items.description: Create AI-powered conversational forms in seconds. Build forms with natural language prompts, collect feedback through chat, and get instant AI insights.

items.name: Plus AI Presentation Agent
items.tagline: AI agent that helps you design PowerPoint slides
items.description: Meet the Plus AI Presentation Agent for PowerPoint. Plus AI doesn‚Äôt just generate slides - it helps you plan your deck, write content, format slides, and edit content directly inside PowerPoint. Using Plus AI's best-in-class PowerPoint editing tools, the Plus AI agent can create presentations from a prompt, rewrite messy slides, and iterate on slide designs via chat. It works directly in PowerPoint and can help you fine-tune slides until they are ready to present. Try it for free today!

items.name: Habit Island
items.description: Habit Island turns your daily habits and goals into a strategy game. Complete tasks, build structures, and earn gems and achievements as your consistency grows your island.

items.name: UnderSurface
items.description: UnderSurface is a journaling app where inner voices respond to your writing in real time. You type. You pause. An inner part reacts. It may notice what you're avoiding, sit with you in discomfort or connect dots you haven't seen yet. It's not a chatbot or a therapist. It's a writing companion. It works in any browser and is multilingual. Strict privacy, export and account controls. Built as a solo project because I kept abandoning my own journal entries the moment they got real.

items.name: Test Your Idea
items.tagline: Find weak spots in your startup idea. Real data, not vibes.
items.description: Stop building something nobody wants. We scan 20+ live data sources and show you what's blocking your idea: competitors, market size, demand signals. Every number links to its source. 1,400+ ideas tested, 9 out of 10 weren't ready.

items.name: PenguinBot AI
items.description: PenguinBot is an action-first AI that turns conversations into real work. It manages emails, schedules tasks, creates documents, and runs workflows automatically. Just tell it what you need ‚Äî it plans, executes, and keeps things moving in the background. Autonomous, secure, and built to run 24/7 so you can focus on what matters.

items.name: UserWants
items.tagline: Stop guessing. Build what users want.
items.description: With UserWants, your users tell you what they actually want. Collect their feedback, let them vote, and focus on building the stuff that actually matters. Simple, minimal, no unnecessary features, just what you need to ship faster.

items.name: Whyze
items.tagline: Understand why users leave your product ‚Äî not just where
items.description: Whyze uses AI to analyze your conversion funnel and explain why users drop off. Get root causes instead of charts and receive actionable insights in seconds.
